  "Description": "PROCESSING:  This Job Loads Data from Sequential File created in xfrm Job and loads into IDS B_INTER_PLN_BILL_DTL table\n                                                                \n     \nMODIFICATIONS:\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                DATASTAGE               CODE                           DATE\nDEVELOPER             DATE                PROJECT                     DESCRIPTION                                                                                      ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW\n-----------------------------    ----------------------     ------------------------------        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\nKalyan Neelam           2015-08-18        5212                               Initial Programming                                                                                IntegrateDev1\n\nAnnotations:\nRead Load File created in the FKEY job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nTruncate and Load B_INTER_PLN_BILL_DTL table\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file"
}